- Bata apa?
- Bata di tangan awak itu.

188
00:19:42,080 --> 00:19:43,440
Saya tak nak buat.

189
00:19:43,520 --> 00:19:44,520
Apa awak cakap?

190
00:19:46,880 --> 00:19:48,080
Ya.

191
00:19:48,160 --> 00:19:49,280
Ya, dia sesuai.

192
00:19:49,360 --> 00:19:50,600
Tak ada saksi.

193
00:19:50,680 --> 00:19:52,400
- Ini tuah orang baru.
- Diam.

194
00:19:52,480 --> 00:19:54,720
Hentak kepala sekali pun dah cukup.

195
